com.sun.xml.ws.commons.virtualbox
Class IUSBDevice

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.xml.ws.commons.virtualbox.IUSBDevice

public class IUSBDevice
extends Object

The IUSBDevice interface represents a virtual USB device attached to the virtual machine. A collection of objects implementing this interface is stored in the IConsole#USBDevices attribute which lists all USB devices attached to a running virtual machine's USB controller.
